          <h3><i class="fas fa-bed-pulse"></i> 傷病給付</h3>
          <p class="occ-benefit-purpose">農民從農時受傷不能工作，補償收入損失</p>
          <div class="occ-benefit-detail">
            <div class="occ-benefit-row">
              <span class="occ-benefit-label">起算日</span>
              <span>自不能工作<strong>第 4 日</strong>起</span>
            </div>
            <div class="occ-benefit-row">
              <span class="occ-benefit-label">期限</span>
              <span>最長 <strong>2 年</strong></span>
            </div>
            <div class="occ-benefit-row">
              <span class="occ-benefit-label">前 2 個月</span>
              <span>月投保金額 × 100% = <strong>每日 680 元</strong></span>
            </div>
            <div class="occ-benefit-row">
              <span class="occ-benefit-label">第 3 個月起</span>
              <span>月投保金額 × 70% = <strong>每日 476 元</strong></span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="occ-benefit-note">
            <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> 需有實際就醫治療紀錄。傷勢轉輕已能從事工作者，僅能申請至恢復工作前 1 日。
          </div>
          <div class="occ-benefit-effective">113/9/1 起適用</div>
        </div>

        <!-- 給付卡片 2：就醫津貼 -->
        <div class="occ-benefit-card">
          <h3><i class="fas fa-hospital"></i> 就醫津貼</h3>
          <p class="occ-benefit-purpose">減輕就醫治療費用負擔（慰問金性質）</p>
          <div class="occ-benefit-detail">
            <div class="occ-benefit-row">
              <span class="occ-benefit-label">門診</span>
              <span><strong>每日 100 元</strong></span>
            </div>
            <div class="occ-benefit-row">
              <span class="occ-benefit-label">住院</span>
              <span><strong>每日 1,200 元</strong></span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="occ-benefit-note">
            <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> 隨傷病給付一併核給，不需另外填寫申請書。
          </div>
          <div class="occ-benefit-effective">114/11/6 起適用</div>
        </div>

        <!-- 給付卡片 3：身心障礙給付 -->
        <div class="occ-benefit-card">
          <h3><i class="fas fa-wheelchair-move"></i> 身心障礙給付</h3>
          <p class="occ-benefit-purpose">因從農致永久身心障礙，補償工作能力減損</p>
          <div class="occ-benefit-detail">
            <div class="occ-benefit-row">
              <span class="occ-benefit-label">金額</span>
              <span>依等級 <strong>15,300 至 612,000 元</strong></span>
            </div>
            <div class="occ-benefit-row">
              <span class="occ-benefit-label">與農保差異</span>
              <span>較農保<strong>增給 50%</strong></span>
