          <h3><i class="fas fa-cross"></i> 喪葬津貼</h3>
          <p class="occ-benefit-purpose">因從農致職業傷病而死亡，補償殯葬費用</p>
          <div class="occ-benefit-detail">
            <div class="occ-benefit-row">
              <span class="occ-benefit-label">金額</span>
              <span>30 個月 × 20,400 = <strong>612,000 元</strong></span>
            </div>
            <div class="occ-benefit-row">
              <span class="occ-benefit-label">與農保差異</span>
              <span>較農保<strong>增給 100%</strong></span>
            </div>
            <div class="occ-benefit-row">
              <span class="occ-benefit-label">請領人</span>
              <span>支出殯葬費之人</span>
