<!-- ========== 區塊 5：加保資格與流程 ========== -->
<div class="occ-sections" id="occ-eligibility">
  <div class="occ-sec-card">
    <div class="occ-sec-header">
      <div class="occ-sec-icon"><i class="fas fa-user-check"></i></div>
      <div>
        <h2>誰能保？怎麼保？</h2>
        <p>三類加保資格與加保流程說明。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="occ-sec-body">
      <div class="occ-eligibility-grid">
        <div class="occ-elig-card">
          <div class="occ-elig-num">1</div>
          <h3>農保被保險人</h3>
          <p class="occ-elig-tag">最大宗</p>
          <p>已參加農保、實際從事農業工作。</p>
          <div class="occ-elig-highlight">
            <i class="fas fa-star"></i> 112/12/1 起，新加入農保者<strong>視為一併參加農職保</strong>（準強制），既有農保被保險人可自願申請。
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="occ-elig-card">
          <div class="occ-elig-num">2</div>
          <h3>健保第三類被保險人</h3>
          <p>已領取相關社會保險老年給付之退休人員（勞、軍、公、教退休人員），及實際從事農業工作之外籍配偶、陸籍配偶。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="occ-elig-card">
          <div class="occ-elig-num">3</div>
          <h3>區域從農零工</h3>
          <p class="occ-elig-tag">110/5/1 起開放</p>
          <p>不具前兩類資格，但以農業專業技術實際從事區域性農業生產工作維生之國民。需檢附從農照片 2 張以上，並列席審查會議說明。</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="occ-common-rules">
        <h3><i class="fas fa-gavel"></i> 共通規定</h3>
        <div class="occ-rules-list">
          <span><i class="fas fa-check"></i> 無年齡上限</span>
          <span><i class="fas fa-check"></i> 須年滿 15 歲</span>
          <span><i class="fas fa-xmark"></i> 不可與軍保、公保、就保、勞保重複加保</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3 class="occ-sub-title"><i class="fas fa-route"></i> 加保流程</h3>
      <div class="occ-step-flow">
        <div class="occ-step">
          <div class="occ-step-num">1</div>
          <div class="occ-step-content">
            <strong>攜帶身分證正本</strong>，到戶籍所在地農會
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="occ-step-arrow"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></div>
        <div class="occ-step">
          <div class="occ-step-num">2</div>
          <div class="occ-step-content">
            填寫<strong>申請表</strong>（農會系統會套印基本資料）
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="occ-step-arrow"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></div>
        <div class="occ-step">
          <div class="occ-step-num">3</div>
          <div class="occ-step-content">
            農會排定<strong>審查會議</strong>進行資格審查
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="occ-step-arrow"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></div>
        <div class="occ-step">
          <div class="occ-step-num">4</div>
          <div class="occ-step-content">
            審查通過當日，農會向<strong>勞保局申報加保</strong>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="occ-step-arrow"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></div>
        <div class="occ-step">
          <div class="occ-step-num">5</div>
          <div class="occ-step-content">
            保險效力<strong>自通知當日零時起算</strong>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="occ-alert-box occ-alert-warn">
        <i class="fas fa-triangle-exclamation"></i>
        <span>須本人親自辦理，不可代辦。</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ========== 區塊 6：申請給付流程 ========== -->
<div class="occ-sections" id="occ-claim">
  <div class="occ-sec-card">
    <div class="occ-sec-header">
      <div class="occ-sec-icon"><i class="fas fa-file-invoice-dollar"></i></div>
      <div>
        <h2>受傷了怎麼申請？</h2>
        <p>從就醫到匯款的完整流程。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="occ-sec-body">
      <div class="occ-step-flow">
        <div class="occ-step occ-step-wide">
          <div class="occ-step-num">1</div>
          <div class="occ-step-content">
            <strong>就醫</strong>
            <div class="occ-step-sub">
              職業傷害：任何醫療院所醫師開立「職業傷害診斷書」<br>
              職業病：職業醫學科專科醫師開立「職業病診斷書」+「評估報告書」
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="occ-step-arrow"><i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i></div>
        <div class="occ-step occ-step-wide">
          <div class="occ-step-num">2</div>
          <div class="occ-step-content">
